1. Giới thiệu và cài đặt Anaconda¶

Anaconda l mt nn tng phn phi min ph ca ngn ng lp trnh Python v R cho tnh ton khoa hc (khoa hc d liu, machine learning, x l d liu ln, phn tch d on, v.v.), nhm mc ch n gin ha vic qun l v trin khai gi. N c trn c Windows, MacOS v Linux.

Anaconda cha tt c cc gi (cng c) ph bin nht m mt nh khoa hc d liu cn. Cc package trong Anaconda c qun l bi trnh qun l ring ca nn tng ny l conda. Ta thng dng conda to mi trng c lp cc d n ca mnh, nhm s dng cc phin bn Python khc nhau hoc cc phin bn package khc nhau, cng nh dng n ci t, g ci t v cp nht cc package ring trong tng d n. Ta c th thy v c bn, conda hot ng gn ging nh pip - trnh qun l gi ca Python.

Anaconda khng ch gm c Python, m cn c hn 600 package m rng i km, l cc package c bn cho cc tc v x l khoa hc d liu nh NumPy, Pandas,.... Bn khng cn phi nhp cc lnh trn terminal ti v na, ch cn ti Anaconda l c th s dng ngay cc package , gip tit kim kh nhiu thi gian cho chng ta.

1.1. Cài đặt Anaconda¶

ci t Anaconda, truy cp vo ng link sau (Individual Edition) ti v ci t phin bn c nhn min ph.

Chn phin bn 64bit hoc 32bit ty thuc vo h iu hnh ang s dng.

Jupyter notebook (file .ipynb) l ti liu kt hp nhiu nh dng: vn bn th, vn bn c nh dng, biu , cng thc, ... v c bit l m thc thi (code) c th c vit bng nhiu ngn ng khc nhau. Jupyter notebook l ti liu ng v c tnh tng tc nn rt ph hp vi cc vn bn, trnh by tnh ton khoa hc. Jupyter notebook cng c th c kt xut ra nhiu nh dng ph bin khc nhau (PDF, HTML, LaTex, ...).

4.1. Vector¶

Mt b gm $n$ s thc (n-tuple) $\boldsymbol{v} = (v_1, v_2, ..., v_n) \in \mathbb{R}^n$ c gi l mt vector kch thc $n$. Cc s $v_1, v_2, ..., v_n \in \mathbb{R}$ c gi l cc phn t (element, entry) ca vector. phn bit vi vector, cc s thc cn c gi l v hng (scalar).

  • to vector, ta c th dng kiu list c sn trn Python bng c php [$v_1$,$v_2$,$\dots$,$v_n$] vi $v_1$,$v_2$,$\dots$,$v_n$ l cc phn t ca vector.
  • Hoc c th s dng hm np.array[] ca th vin numpy bng c php [$v_1$,$v_2$,$\dots$,$v_n$].
  • Hoc c th s dng hm Matrix([]) ca th vin sympy, vi vector s c biu din di dng ct.

Khi mun truy cp mt phn t bt k trong vector, ta gi tn ca vector t v km theo ch s th t ca phn t cn xut. Vi lu trong python, s th t ca phn t trong vector c nh du t 0 n n-1 hoc t -n n -1.

Quy định chấm bài¶

Nhng trng hp sau y s b 0 im ton b n:

  • Np sai quy nh
  • Khng c bo co
  • Thc thi m ngun bo li

**LU : SAO CHP BI LM CA NHAU S B 0 IM TON B PHN THC HNH**

H PTTT $A\boldsymbol{x} = \boldsymbol{b}$ thng c gii bng cc bc:

Bc 1. Lp ma trn b sung (augmented matrix) bng cch ghp ct $\boldsymbol{b}$ sau ma trn $A$: $\bar{A} = \left[ A | \boldsymbol{b} \right]$.

Bc 2. Dng cc php bin i s cp trn dng bin i $\bar{A}$ thnh ma trn tng ng dng c dng bc thang $R$.

Bc 3. Gii $R$ bng php th ngc (back-substitution) c nghim.

Phép khử Gauss¶

Kh Gauss (Gaussian elimination) l mt cch bin i tng ng dng a ma trn v dng bc thang. Thut gii gm cc bc:

Bc 1. Xc nh ct tri nht khng cha ton s 0.

Bc 2. i ch hai dng, nu cn thit, a s hng khc 0 no di v u ct nhn c Bc 1.
(n gin nht, c th chn dng u tin c s hng khc 0. Phc tp hn, chin lc "partial pivoting" chn dng c s hng c tr tuyt i ln nht.)

Bc 3. Vi s hng u ct nhn c t Bc 2 l $a \neq 0$, nhn dng cha n vi $\frac{1}{a}$ c s dn u 1 (leading 1).
(Bc ny ty chn.)

Bc 4. Cng mt bi s thch hp ca dng u cho tng dng di bin cc s hng bn di s dn u thnh 0.

Bc 5. Che dng u lm xong. Lp li cc bc cho n khi c ma trn bc thang.

In [1]:
import math
def is_zero(x):
    "kim tra s thc x c l s thc 0 (rt gn 0)"
    return math.isclose(x, 0, abs_tol=1e-09)

def mul_scalar_vector(alpha, v):
    return [alpha*vi for vi in v]

def add_vector(v, w):
    return [vi + wi for vi, wi in zip(v, w)]

def row_switch(A, i, k):
    "di <-> dk"
    A[i], A[k] = A[k], A[i]
    
def row_mul(A, i, alpha):
    "di = anpha*di"
    A[i] = mul_scalar_vector(alpha, A[i])

def row_add(A, i, k, alpha):
    "di = di + anpha*dk"
    A[i] = add_vector(A[i], mul_scalar_vector(alpha, A[k]))
In [2]:
def Gauss_elimination(A):
    R = A.copy()
    n_row, n_col = len(R), len(R[0]) # kch thc ma trn
    row = col = 0
    while row < n_row:
        # Bc 1
        while col < n_col and all(is_zero(R[i][col]) for i in range(row, n_row)):
            col += 1
        if col == n_col: #  c dng bc thang
            break
        
        # Bc 2 (chn dng u tin c s hng khc 0)
        pivot_row = row + [not is_zero(R[i][col]) for i in range(row, n_row)].index(True)
        row_switch(R, row, pivot_row)
        
        # Bc 3
        row_mul(R, row, 1/R[row][col])
            
        # Bc 4
        for i in range(row + 1, n_row):
            row_add(R, i, row, -R[i][col])
    
        # Bc 5
        row += 1
    return R

import sympy
def back_substitution(R):
    "R l ma trn bc thang ca ma trn b sung ca h phng trnh Ax = b"
    n_row, n_col = len(R), len(R[0]) # kch thc ma trn R
    
    # vector nghim (danh sch theo th t n)
    sol = [None for _ in range(n_col - 1)]
    
    # Tm dng di cng khc khng
    row = n_row - 1
    while row >= 0 and all(is_zero(R[row][j]) for j in range(n_col)):
        row -= 1
    
    if row >= 0 and [not is_zero(R[row][j]) for j in range(n_col)].index(True) == n_col - 1:
        print("H phng trnh tuyn tnh v nghim") # v nghim
        return None
    
    last_pcol = n_col - 1
    while row >= 0:
        pcol = [not is_zero(R[row][j]) for j in range(n_col)].index(True)
        for i in range(pcol, last_pcol): # cc n t do
            sol[i] = sympy.symbols(f"x{i + 1}")
        sol[pcol] = R[row][n_col - 1] - sum(R[row][j]*sol[j] for j in range(pcol + 1, n_col - 1))
        last_pcol = pcol
        row -= 1
    
    # B sung cc n t do t 0 n last_pcol - 1
    for i in range(0, last_pcol):
        sol[i] = sympy.symbols(f"x{i + 1}")
    return sol
